name: What to whitelist?
---
body:

## What to Allow?

* Only allow a single expression
  <pre>assert len(module.body) == 1 and isinstance(module.body[0], ast.Expr)</pre>
* Filter any `ast.Call` instances
  <pre>assert call.func.id in ("any", "all")</pre>
* Filter access to dunder attributes
    <pre>assert not attr.attr.startswith("__")</pre>
---
